 "arabic", "text_bw": "mino gayori taxal~uli", "text_ar": "مِنْ غَيْرِ تَخَلُّلِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Without interruption."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txl~l AlmaTaru", "text_ar": "تخلّل المَطَرُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The rain was confined to a particular place,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "to particular places; was not general."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K.) ―         -b4-  See also 1, in two places, in the former half of the paragraph. ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txl~l Alr~uTaba", "text_ar": "تخلّل الرُّطَبَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He sought out the fresh ripe dates in the interstices of the roots of the branches"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "after the cutting off of the racemes of fruit."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "txl~l Aln~axolapa", "text_ar": "تخلّل النَّخْلَةَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He picked the dates that were among the roots of the branches of the palm-tree;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "takar~abahaA", "text_ar": "تَكَرَّبَهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (AHn, TA.) ―         -b6-  For other significations, see 2, in four places."}], "source_refs": ["M", "K"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}